title: Will the Black Ferns break through the French Blue Wall?

media:group.media:title: Will the Black Ferns break through the French Blue Wall?
media:group.media:description:
The Black Ferns will take on France in a showdown of epic proportions at Eden Park with the winner booking a place in the RWC2021 Final! Can hosts keep up their unbeatable pace against a staunch French defence?
